description:
Blackbird has a sign that just says "Bar". This can be confusing to someone who is familiar with the Bar on Church and tries to give directions to said "Bar". Especially if this person is not on Facebook. This is why;

The Blackbird was the Metro before the Metro became the Lookout and Expansion became Metro which should NEVER be confused with Bar on Church which was The Transfer until Bar on Castro became Bar on Church and Q took over Bar on Castro. 

Oh, Blackbird aka "Bar" makes some fancy cocktails that taste good. They also have a nice mixed crowd, a pool table and a great happy hour. Hopefully you can find the place to experience this.
